com.intel.fightclub.dialog.alarms

Class DialogueEngineFightClubAlarm

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.alarms.DialogueEngineFightClubAlarm

  • @ThreadSafe
public final class DialogueEngineFightClubAlarm
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of an alarm to be sent to the dialogue engine. with all specific Fight Club errors notified to SLAM using alarms.
